echo $now-&gt;toString('\Y\e\a\r: Y');</p>

<p>Expected:</p>

<p>Year: 2010</p>

<p>Result:</p>

<p>\2010\System/Localtime\PM\Fri, 16 Jul 2010 14:42:22 +0300: 2010</p>

